reviewText: I'll write a review when I can stop laughing . . .
I've always enjoyed all of Anita's other DVD's, so there is no reason to doubt I'll enjoy this new one.
This is one her best DVDs to date!  The material is great and everyone I've shown it to, loved it!
This DVD came totally corrupted.  Could not view at all!  I would Not RECOMMEND!
This lady makes me laugh so hard my face hurts!
If you want to laugh-her observations are honest- well presented- and funny!
I enjoyed this one a lot. Her work is always funny.
Anita has come into her own with this video. Her singing, music and stand up comedy is a great way to spend the evening with your family.
Anita is very funny! This is humor that is not offensive, and it pokes fun at the aging process! It will bring many laughs!

I have always enjoyed Anita Renfroe but this one was a disappointment. She was on a cruise ship, which i was not aware of when I purchased. I think this had a great impact on her material used. I chose also based on other reviews but none stated it was on a cruise. Please consider this before purchasing.

Very Funny - watched with my mother in law and my aunt as well as my husband and step-father in law.  Everyone laughed and enjoyed the DVD.  Good, Clean humor.  Definitely geared toward women, but our men appreciated the humor as well.
Bought as a birthday gift for my wife, she laughed long and loud.
